& [SLMSlice26ProviderDisagreementPayloads] is the source-complete slice for typed provider disagreement payloads
  + [slice_id] is SLM-26
  + [status] is source_complete_policy_gated
  + [effort] is S-M
  + [risk] is medium
  + [depends_on] is SLM-05, SLM-17, SLM-22
  + [contract] is slm_project/specifications/contracts/SLM_Provider_Disagreement_Payload_Contract.sop
  + [deliverable] is typed provider objection and answer payload fields
  + [completion_review] is slm_project/planning/project_manager/reviews/SLM_Manager_Batch_Review_2026-06-21.sop

  & [WorkCompleted] is the slice result
    + [added] is disagreement_class field on provider suggestions
    + [added] is answer_kind field on provider suggestions
    + [added] is constructors for typed objections and typed answers
    + [updated] is deliberation classification to consume provider payloads

  & [RemainingGate] is executable verification
    + [blocked_by] is Windows Application Control policy for Cargo-generated executables
    + [allowed_validation] is source scan and SOP review only
